create relatively hard working and living conditions. He said
doctors must exhibit great courage in order to overcome
difficulties and provide medical services.
</P>
<P>
Stability and development in Tibet are important to overall
stability and development of the country, said Li, adding that
sending the medical team to the region shows the great concern the
Party and central government have for Tibetans.
</P>
<P>
