Kaiserslautern and its seismological station in Sonesca, Spain,
will be cut back but not closed, the statement said.
</P>
<P>
In Israel, Fleet Hospital, Enshemer, managed by the U.S. Navy
Europe, will be closed, the Pentagon said. 
